column5: Everyone needs one of these. Else a jet pack!
Harry, that's what I need.   I'd probably kill myself Is that Wayne flying that thing?
I dont know it. Looks like fun
I would do it in a heartbeat. Dad was a Catalina and Sunderland pilot, flying boats are in my blood!
I thought it might great to have one but they want $20,000 for the one in the video   vance
That thing would be nice for puddle jumping a lot of smaller inaccessible lakes in Northern Ontario, but at $ 20,000. a pop, Yikes!
